Package: ezTrack
Type: Package
Title: ezTrack: an R Package with tools to enable exploration of animal movement data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Taylor", 
           family = "Craft", 
           email = "taylor.b.craft2@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A lightweight and user-friendly toolkit for importing, cleaning, summarizing,
    analyzing, and mapping animal tracking data. Supports raw CSV or Excel input,
    calculates movement summaries and home ranges (MCP or KDE), and renders
    interactive Leaflet maps.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
